line to have media monitoring set. This field MUST have been obtained by
sending the <a href="2759c744-e040-4c5d-b4b5-215d391f0490" data-linktype="relative-path">Open</a>
packet.</p><p><b>dwMediaModes (4 bytes): </b>An unsigned 32-bit
